      "parameters": {
        "content": "## alice-dms-scanner\n\nScheduled hourly (07:00-22:00).\n\nScans NAS folders from alice.dms_watched_folders,\nfinds new documents, checks dedup via Redis,\nverifies file stability (5s wait),\nchecks PDF text layer for OCR needs,\npublishes to MQTT alice/dms/new.\n\n### Redis Key Pattern\n- `alice:dms:processed:{hash}` = already processed\n- `alice:dms:queued:{hash}` = in queue\n\n### Dedup Note\nUses Redis GET/SET with individual keys per hash\ninstead of SISMEMBER/SADD (n8n Redis node v1\ndoes not support set operations natively).",
        "width": 360,
        "height": 380
